<view class="page">
  <view class="card hero-card">
    <view class="hero-text">
      <view class="hero-title">奔腾特勤队预约服务</view>
      <view class="hero-subtitle">每周六晚 19:00-21:00 提供值班支持，地点请以实际通知为准。</view>
      <view class="hero-btn-row">
        <button class="primary-btn hero-btn hero-btn-half" bindtap="goCreateBooking">立即预约</button>
        <button class="ghost-btn hero-btn hero-btn-half" bindtap="goQueryBooking">查询预约</button>
      </view>
    </view>
    <image class="hero-image" src="/assets/banner.png" mode="aspectFill" />
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="section-title">当前选中日期概览</view>
    <view class="section-subtitle">默认展示最近一次开放预约的周六：{{selectedDateLabel}}</view>
    <view class="stats-grid top-gap">
      <view class="stat-item">
        <view class="stat-value">{{summary.totalCount}}</view>
        <view class="stat-label">总名额</view>
      </view>
      <view class="stat-item">
        <view class="stat-value blue">{{summary.availableCount}}</view>
        <view class="stat-label">剩余名额</view>
      </view>
      <view class="stat-item">
        <view class="stat-value orange">{{summary.bookedCount}}</view>
        <view class="stat-label">已预约</view>
      </view>
      <view class="stat-item">
        <view class="stat-value green">{{summary.completedCount}}</view>
        <view class="stat-label">已完成</view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="section-title">本学期累计概览</view>
    <view class="section-subtitle">从学期开始日期起统计累计预约与结单数量。</view>
    <view class="stats-grid top-gap">
      <view class="stat-item">
        <view class="stat-value orange">{{semesterSummary.bookedCount}}</view>
        <view class="stat-label">累计已预约</view>
      </view>
      <view class="stat-item">
        <view class="stat-value green">{{semesterSummary.completedCount}}</view>
        <view class="stat-label">累计已结单</view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="section-title">未来值班安排</view>
    <view class="list-gap">
      <block wx:for="{{scheduleOverview}}" wx:key="serviceDate" wx:for-item="schedule">
        <view class="schedule-item">
          <view class="schedule-top">
            <view>
              <view class="schedule-title">{{schedule.serviceDateLabel}}</view>
              <view class="schedule-desc">{{schedule.description}}</view>
            </view>
            <view class="schedule-count">{{schedule.summaryText}}</view>
          </view>
          <view class="slot-row">
            <block wx:for="{{schedule.slots}}" wx:key="id" wx:for-item="slot">
              <view class="slot-pill slot-pill-{{slot.status}}">{{slot.label}} {{slot.statusText}}</view>
            </block>
          </view>
        </view>
      </block>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="section-title">服务说明</view>
    <view class="info-line">1. 当前仅开放周六 19:00-21:00 的两个预约时段，每个时段最多 10 人。</view>
    <view class="info-line">2. 提交预约前需阅读并同意《隐私政策》《用户协议》。</view>
    <view class="info-line">3. 服务人员权限已改为管理员审批制，管理员权限已改为 OpenID 白名单控制。</view>
  </view>
</view>
